casebody.data:
No. 679. William Beattie & Son, Petitioner, v. United Shirt and Collar Company et al. April 29, 1907. Mr. George A. Mosher and Mr. Frank S. Black for petitioner. Mr. Livingston Gifford and Mr. Hillary C. Messimer for respondents.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.
